9. The miter saw of claim 1, wherein:
said elongate fence body includes a base attachment portion and a sliding portion;
said base attachment portion is fixed to said base;
said sliding portion includes said first connecting structure; and
said sliding portion is slidably supported on said base attachment portion for sliding movement parallel to said first axis between a first position and a second position, said second position providing clearance for said saw assembly to perform bevel cuts.
